  <h1>About Nepô</h1>

  <p>From 🇧🇷, grew up in the 🇺🇸, with a 🇯🇵 family, Nepô is an Information Architect & Designer and the founder of <a href="https://mee.cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mee</a> — a knowledge management platform built to organise information in a visual way. A self-described Library Sciences nerd and confirmed bookworm across Fantasy, Biography, History and Design.</p>

  <p>With 15 years in the presentation industry working with clients like Gartner, NVIDIA and Blizzard, and having worked across 10+ countries, he has delivered over 100 conferences, workshops, symposiums and summits. As a speaker on Technology, Information Architecture and Design, he has run presentation workshops for startups and enterprise companies around the world.</p>

  <p>Beyond slides, Nepô was a partner at <a href="https://lilo.zone" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lilo.Zone</a>, a creative studio and maker space with a community of 30+ artists, architects and engineers. He spent a decade supporting <a href="https://diatipo.com.br" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DiaTipo TypeCon</a>, Brazil's largest typography conference, and has contributed to the <a href="https://futuretextpublishing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Future of Text</a> symposium and book.</p>

